     <body>
     <div type="to_the_author">
   <head>To the Author.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>I Read thy <hi>Poems,</hi> and I them admire;</l>
      <l>The more I reade, the more I do desire:</l>
      <l>They breathe such holy <hi>Passions</hi> in the mind;</l>
      <l>Who reades them most, himselfe shall better find.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>R. C.</signed>
   </closer>
   <trailer>FINIS.</trailer>
   <pb facs="31"/>
</div>
